\begin_inset Formula $\mathsf{E}[deg_{E}(m)^{2}]=r\log(M)(\frac{M-1}{M})(\frac{M-r\log(M)}{M})+(r\log(M)\frac{M-1}{M})^{2}\leq r\log(M)+(r\log(M))^{2}$
\end_inset

.
